ui.landscapeDescription:
An interactive gateway to explore interconnected biological data. Major biological entities (Genes, Proteins, Tissues, Cell Lines, Compounds, and Drugs) act as interactive nodes, each represented as distinct entry points into their respective data spaces. 
 
 For example, users can:
 1. Enter the Genes workbench and select specific genes of interest
 2. Visualize these genes' expression level in various tissues types via GTEx Tissues workbench
 3. Explore or visualise gene co-expression levels
